{"type": "article", "id": 20008, "title": "大理石表盘的手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174319YIWgS1BaJUsvyf9x.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款手表用了非常漂亮的大理石做表盘，有黑色和白色两种，上面没有具体的刻度只留下细致而自然的纹路。大理石的天然和厚重可以反衬出手表的精细，让这款表显得珍贵。手表连接了黑色的真皮表带，在传统中让它显得轻盈。设计方来自悉尼的工作室 Horse，售价 229 美元，<a href=\"http://www.thehorse.com.au/collections/time-tellers/#the-stone\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150326lRgN62rFdspS5Xx7.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1007\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22804878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150326vtQ3RWz6aVSmeu4d.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1007\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22804878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150327uWZrIvx3YyEobMiw.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1007\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22804878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150327bIxOJEmMrg426vGD.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1007\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22804878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}